ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Revoking Order in Council P.C. 1997-124
PrecisOrder (1) revoking Order in Council P.C. 1997-124 of January 28, 1997 as amended by P.C 2010-1092 of September 2, 2010; (2) determining as special service, within the meaning of those Regulations, service that meets certains conditions; and (3) specifiying that the Bar that is awarded with the SPECIAL SERVICE MEDAL, representing the special service referred to in paragraph (b) is to bear the words "HUMANITAS".
